{"product_id":"maceta-vida-elementos-agua-viento-fuego-decoracion-impresa-en-3d","title":"VIDA Pot – Elements (Water · Wind · Fire) – 3D Printed Decoration","description":"\u003cp\u003eDecorative pot from the VIDA collection, individually manufactured using 3D printing in our workshop in Spain. Each piece is printed separately, checked before shipping, and features a clean finish with careful details. This model is not mass-produced and cannot be found with this configuration and characteristics in conventional stores.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003e🌱 \u003cstrong\u003eShipping with plant and seeds\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSpain:\u003c\/strong\u003e Includes real plant and seeds (optional, indicate in order notes).\u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eInternational:\u003c\/strong\u003e Due to phytosanitary regulations, shipments outside of Spain do not include plants or seeds. Includes a small 3D-printed decorative plant which, although it does not replace the beauty of a real plant, makes the product look just as good. The product is exactly the same; only the live contents of the package change.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e📌 \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/makermur.com\/pages\/normativa-fitosanitaria\"\u003eCheck MAKER-MUR's phytosanitary policy\u003c\/a\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e⚠️ Note: The included plant—real or decorative—is an exclusive complement to the VIDA collection and cannot be exchanged for any other product or monetary compensation.\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MAKER-MUR","offers":[{"title":"💧 Water ·","offer_id":53732377624915,"sku":"VIDA-ELEM-AGUA","price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"🌀 Wind","offer_id":53732482711891,"sku":"VIDA-ELEM-VIENTO","price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"🔥 Fire","offer_id":53732482744659,"sku":"VIDA-ELEM-FUEGO","price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/file